             was indicted for <rs id="t18151025-111-off655" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18151025-111-off655" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18151025-111-off655" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18151025-111-victim967" type="victimName">
                           Stephen 
                           Node
