                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151025-111-defend965 t18151025-111-punish658"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 22.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
